+--------------------------------------------------------------------+

An anonymous reader writes "Recently Hal Leonard Corporation, the world's
largest songbook publisher, sent an email to the music publishing and
copyright community urging them not to license guitar tablature for free,
advertising-supported use online. The email includes a number of factual
errors and was potentially very damaging to the potential for a free,
legal, and licensed destination for guitar tab online. Musicnotes and
MXTabs have [0]posted the full letter along with their response."

